Enhanced WhatsApp Messaging Channel Activation Checklist

After you create an enhanced WhatsApp channel on the Messaging Settings page, you canâ€™t yet message with customers in the channel. Run through this checklist to verify that your channel is ready for business. Then, activate the channel to start helping customers in WhatsApp.

This article applies only to Enhanced WhatsApp channels.

**Required Steps:**

* Give users access to Messaging by assigning them the necessary permissions.
* Set up message routing preferences and configure the Service Console.
* Customize auto-responses and keywords for common scenarios.

**Recommended Steps:**

* Create messaging user records for existing customers to preserve their consent preferences.
* Create an enhanced bot to lighten the load on human service agents.
* Set up automated message notifications and copy message templates.
* Create a library of interactive content for agents and bots.

After completing these steps, you can activate your channel by clicking Activate Channel in the Messaging Settings page.
